378
00:23:17,760 --> 00:23:18,680
From Guizhou.

379
00:23:20,239 --> 00:23:21,920
So you have the address on his ID?

380
00:23:30,800 --> 00:23:32,359
Excuse me, do you have anyone

381
00:23:32,439 --> 00:23:33,560
named Li Lu here?

382
