Li Lu resigned a year ago.

383
00:23:36,079 --> 00:23:37,239
He also moved.

384
00:23:37,479 --> 00:23:38,599
No one knows where he is now.

385
00:23:38,680 --> 00:23:39,640
One year ago.

386
00:23:40,719 --> 00:23:43,000
