436
00:25:35,079 --> 00:25:35,920
Hello.

437
00:25:36,000 --> 00:25:37,040
Mr. Lin?

438
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:42,839
Hello.

439
00:25:44,439 --> 00:25:45,520
